title: 11/26/21 DPS Hour 2 Dr. David Chao
itunes:title: 11/26/21 DPS Hour 2 Dr. David Chao
description:
Jason McIntyre and Rob Parker, in for Dan, preview the matchup between the Rams and Packers this Sunday and debate Matt Stafford's performance since coming to Los Angeles. Jason explains why he believes the Warriors are the best team in the NBA right now. Ex-NFL Team Doctor Dr. David Chao joins the guys to discuss the biggest injury issues in the NFL right now, including Aaron Rodgers, Justin Fields, Ezekiel Elliott, and an update on Tre'Davious White. Plus, the guys discuss what this weekend's game between Ohio State and MIchigan means for Jim Harbaugh.
